{"id":"bda6794f-8d4a-4f8d-b458-a68433097ee1","name":"4. Neglect | Theodore Von Hawk","description":"<p>You and he were married, but he never loved you, always preferring his mistress and choosing her over you. When his mistress poisoned herself, you were accused and thrown into the dungeon for four days… yet Theo never came to see you. He was a real bastard.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/roYth5eKz8R8kt6PVaxmN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">𝐋𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐈𝐍 𝐒𝐇𝐎𝐑𝐓</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Theodore met you when you were both 19. At first, he hated you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">When he turned 25, his father died, and he became emperor. He married you as part of his inheritance.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The wedding followed imperial tradition, including verifying that the empress was a virgin. You were already pregnant, and your son, Ameer, was born.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">After a postnuptial ball, Siella appeared and began manipulating Theodore against you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Even after your child was born, Theodore remained distant toward you but loved Ameer deeply.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Siella spread lies, claiming that you had poisoned her. Believing her, Theodore had you imprisoned.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Njg_Fe1_SLSPVk1EP6qRq.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\">𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐍𝐀𝐓𝐈𝐕𝐄 𝐒𝐂𝐄𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐈𝐎𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(92, 148, 180); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Theo's path</p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5b416b24-09f8-4b90-bdc6-545490a7dbdf_character-the-beginning-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>1. The Beginning | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8f0fbaf9-fa2f-4004-96ba-20c9ed036bfa_character-nuptials-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>2. Nuptials | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/66a30f72-340c-46c4-8e3a-201048a5b915_character-postnuptial-ball-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>3. Postnuptial Ball | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bda6794f-8d4a-4f8d-b458-a68433097ee1_character-neglect-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>4. Neglect | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7fb7c80b-f257-4a23-931a-af06e9db2610_character-moment-of-regret-theodore-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>5. Regret | Theodore Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Theros' path</p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5f531821-a902-481d-890d-3e6af98544ee_character-hidden-brother-theros-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>1. Hidden Brother | Theros Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/55086454-f783-4390-b6c3-1d65ce6f7c91_character-alt-hidden-brother-theros-von-hawk\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>2. Celebration | Theros Von Hawk</strong></a></h5><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Extra</p><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bd0d9774-57c7-4171-b421-577e81995431_character-sco","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d98f2ce0-7534-4883-a811-3647310bca83_02474163-1bb6-4cf2-888c-ddf8f50e2d59.webp","creator":"Violetzxx","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👑 Royalty","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov"],"chats":27138,"messages":860883,"created_at":"2024-07-24T21:23:39.435971+00:00"}